    10	## Key Discovery: Structural Mismatch
    11	
    12	**The polynomial product P(z) does NOT encode the Legendre sieve.**
    13	
    14	- P(z) has nonzero coefficients at **subset-SUM** positions of primes (additive structure)
    15	- The Legendre sieve formula needs **subset-PRODUCT** divisors of the primorial (multiplicative structure)
    16	- FFT operates on power series (additive exponents) and cannot accelerate Dirichlet convolution (multiplicative structure)
